{"tid":1393892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［呼召大西北力量］8月5號西鐵線有冇得玩？","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:24:10.000Z","uid":134141,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ab057e322b0b2b0c7398ec0ef78e4f4fb1c527","tid":1393892,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"出面好似冇巴絲提過要塞西鐵線<br />\n但大西北總人口有成150萬Up<br />\n如果成功比大西北勞動人口出到紅磡九龍<br />\n成個罷工不合作運動既效益會大大減低<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以大家唔應該咁易放棄西鐵線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n聽閒西鐵線有後備路軌<br />\n所以好難成功塞到西鐵線<br />\n有冇做港鐵或者知內情既巴絲<br />\n知道塞邊幾個西鐵站最有效益<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月5號 一定要塞埋西鐵線</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eefba0e7153da4e7c2370e92511b28992c4e60f","tid":1393892,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ed6d11759fffa51e662de960e90059d352f9a8","tid":1393892,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36db09f8acf9f4ef67390f966254c1d928cab9b","tid":1393892,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db870a380622912ea4e8a0d647b20b9b36310ea","tid":1393892,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},